{
  "texts": [
    "Mouse monoclonal antiserum against the LPS core (Hycult Biotechnology), sheep anti-mouse horseradish peroxidase (HRP) conjugate secondary antibody (GE Amersham) and mouse anti-His tag HRP conjugate antibody (BioLegend) were used for the immunoblots.",
    "Bands were visualized using the ECL Prime Western blotting detection reagent (GE Amersham) and the Azure c400 imaging system.",
    "Uncropped immunoblots are provided in Supplementary Fig. 1.",
    "Genes encoding LptB, LptC and LptFG were amplified by PCR from A. baylyi ADP1 (ATCC 33305) genomic DNA.",
    "lptB and lptFG PCR products were inserted into pCDFduet by Gibson assembly (New England Biolabs) to generate plasmids analogous to those used for other LptB 2 FG homologues 55."
  ]
}